<div class="panel">
	<% if (!recipeCount) { %>
		<h3 class="panelTitle">You're new round here, right?</h3>
		<p>It doesn't look like you've used this app before. Let's get you setup.</p>
		<p>You'll need some recipes. Do you want to create a new one from scratch or do you want to import some defaults?</p>
		<button class="button-fullWidth js-createRecipe">Create a new recipe</button>
		<button class="button-fullWidth js-loadDefaults">Load in some defaults</button>
	<% } else { %>
		<h3 class="panelTitle">Nothing's brewing. We should change that.</h3>
		<button class="button-fullWidth button-spaced js-viewRecipes">Pick a recipe to brew from</button>
	<% } %>
</div>
